data.description: Charming 4-Bedroom, 3-Bathroom Retreat in Knight Forest  Welcome to your tranquil oasis in the coveted Knight Forest neighborhood! This beautiful 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home sits on an expansive 1.81-acre lot, offering a serene escape from the hustle and bustle of city life. The seller is generously offering $4,000 in concessions to sweeten the deal, making it even more enticing.  Key Features:  Sprawling Outdoor Paradise: Enjoy the great outdoors from the comfort of your screened-in back porch or the expansive custom deck, perfect for al fresco dining and entertaining. Three custom-built storage sheds/workshops provide ample space for hobbies and storage.  Natural Beauty: Tucked away amidst lush green grass and towering trees, this home offers a private and peaceful setting. It's the ideal haven for nature lovers and those seeking a quiet retreat.  Cozy Living: The spacious living room is centered around a grand fireplace, creating a warm and inviting focal point. Large windows overlook the back porch, allowing natural light to flood the space and provide tranquil views of the outdoors.  Entertainer's Dream: The separate dining area offers plenty of room for hosting gatherings and special occasions. The well-appointed kitchen features numerous cabinets and a central bar area, making meal prep and casual dining a breeze.  Comfortable Living Spaces: With four bedrooms, this home provides ample space for family and guests. One bedroom has been transformed into a walk-in closet, but it can easily be converted back into a bedroom to suit your needs. Down the hall, you'll find three additional bedrooms and two well-appointed bathrooms.  Convenient Amenities: The third full bathroom, complete with a shower, is conveniently located at the entry of the garage, making cleanup after outdoor activities a breeze. The adjacent spacious laundry room adds to the practicality of this home.  This home is brimming with potential and offers a peaceful and harmonious lifestyle. Don't miss your chance to make it your own! Schedule a private showing today and take advantage of the seller's generous $4,000 concession. Your dream home awaits!
